@chapter GtkHScale
A horizontal slider widget for selecting a value from a range

@section Overview
The @code{<gtk-hscale>} widget is used to allow the user to select a value using
a horizontal slider. To create one, use @code{gtk-hscale-new-with-range}.

The position to show the current value, and the number of decimal places shown
can be set using the parent @code{<gtk-scale>} class's functions.

